datasources.datasource: set lc_numeric = 'it_IT.UTF-8'; select sb.key_linea as keylinea, sb.key_bancale as keybancale, sb.bntpspe as tpspe, sb.bncdlin as cdlin, sb.bnnmbnc as numero_bancale, sb.bnnmced as cedola, count(sc.key_bancale) as numero_colli, to_char(sum(case sc.cppsrea when 0 then sc.cppspre else sc.cppsrea end )::float/1000,'9999990D999') as peso_colli from storico_bancali sb inner join storico_colli_bancale sc on sc.key_bancale=sb.key_bancale where sb.key_bancale=$P{key_bancale} group by keylinea, keybancale, tpspe, cdlin, numero_bancale, cedola;
